{"tid":2468513,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本Falcom】綜合討論區Vol.67【- 點解要去打科興 -】","createTime":"2021-03-30T14:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T19:21:21.000Z","uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5180987547813f1734bf46f105683d53d6fd252a","tid":2468513,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSTB3mYcLrcHS787c2TkVUEEDsKdZxFbDKBQdAoYbcRj9?filename=j7B3nfT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7B3nfT.gif&h=4467bef6&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"2a179b9537c69eeac2c0fb0bd70617f405b1b3ca","tid":2468513,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:02:32.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/153412_b1eb08ecb8ac9ec4d76a902cf9e3d486.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F153412_b1eb08ecb8ac9ec4d76a902cf9e3d486.gif&h=dab1a390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins><span class=\"gold\">Falcom 3大柱</span></ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTKrawE3x77spJzSZuY1f27bZ8rwbrGmmyQhaaHF5yFxf?filename=cPdjKs2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPdjKs2.jpg&h=5d3be7d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">軌跡系列</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYqdrXdQzZQVdbT89Z2QgmXyVmPAHE8n3n3hWy5xf9ak5?filename=0N3NrmQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0N3NrmQ.png&h=e50b737a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"orange\">伊蘇系列</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVXAdLDjLdU11sRk9HBxN48TZKFq55MdR8exwCBCCs5Pj?filename=aLK6taP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLK6taP.jpg&h=03e923b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><del>幻都</del>404系列</span></p><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"red\">軌跡系列</span></ins><br />\n目前由4篇章 - 10集構成 由零軌開始脫離英雄傳說系列嘅編號<br />\n先後次序由 空軌FC -&gt; SC -&gt; 3rd -&gt; 零軌 -&gt; 碧軌 -&gt; 閃I -&gt; II -&gt; III -&gt; IV -&gt; 創軌 -&gt;黎軌<br />\n外加曉/星軌 時間由零碧中間開始  仲有神作 - 羈絆 &amp; OL<br />\n軌跡系列網站<a href=\"https://www.falcom.co.jp/kiseki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.falcom.co.jp%2Fkiseki%2F&d=T8vHa4Omq%2F1xxkbvjwgdjm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=609337f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.falcom.co.jp/kiseki/</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"orange\">伊蘇系列</span></ins><br />\n目前共9集 包括伊蘇I - II , 伊蘇III (菲爾佳娜之誓) , 伊蘇IV (塞爾塞塔的樹海) , 伊蘇V (失落的砂之都凱芬) , 伊蘇VI (納比斯汀的方舟) , 伊蘇VII , 伊蘇VIII (丹娜的隕涕日) , 伊蘇 始源<br />\n伊蘇系列除咗I - II外 其他都無實質嘅遊玩次序<br />\n新作 伊蘇Ⅸ -Monstrum NOX- 已於2019年9月推出<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"violet\"><del>幻都</del>404系列</span></ins><br />\n雖然只有5集 但係3大柱之中最歷史悠久 最初同英雄傳說一樣都屬於屠龍者系列<br />\n<del>最新作 東京幻都 社長有意再獨立系列化</del> 垃圾 無人權"},{"pid":"00b09211bacd557901c9ed37b3bc88be7ecc2313","tid":2468513,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"<ins>2021年</ins><br />\n黎之軌跡    平台未定   日期未定<br />\n那由多之軌跡    平台PS4   日期未定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2022年</ins><br />\n東幼2"},{"pid":"bb1f8e264b1ffd828cc3225a2e24d98a716d81ea","tid":2468513,"uid":52423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"懷念牙軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f19cc8c0f116e8260fdaff561ff36085a3f0dfa","tid":2468513,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed344e2699e653614afe18e2fc6b62d191bda5bd","tid":2468513,"uid":173404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"2022 <br />\n東幻2？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}